snippet.textDisplay:
This took me to the heavens, to the amusement parks as a kid, to the time i was in highschool playing music in the car and being careless of life, when life was piling up to responsibilities, gave me ecstatic orgasm in the mind. I almost forgot how beautiful music can be. This is the most beautiful song of the 21st century that came out of this country. This gave Bangladesh the identity it was missing. 
Nobody can beat this.
